title: 2015 Tootie Mix in Review
description:
The 2015 Tootie Mix in Review is a "Greatest Hits" mix of music taken from 2015 monthly Tootie mixes, if you will. There's something from every mix. It also includes Tootie's 2015 "Song of the Year": Pearl Jam's "Black", which has been newly re-individualized with impressive results. If you only listen to one Tootie Mix this year, this is the one to listen to.

Most tracks are sourced from lossless material. All of the compilations' songs utilize playback gain values from Tootie's personal volume-leveling procedure, resulting in a consistent overall listening experience without the need to adjust the volume between songs. The method focuses on vocal volume.
